        <inline name="agenda item name">Protection of persons in the event of disasters</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 9 December 2021</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#sixthCommittee">[on the report of the Sixth Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/76/495, para. 7</inline>)]</docProponent>
